    "c-label": {
      "type": "elementHeading",
      "level": 6,
      "text": "THREE CASE STUDIES",
      "align": "left",
      "width": "hug",
      "height": "hug",
      "marginBottom": "0.5rem"
    },
    "c-img-1": {
      "type": "elementImage",
      "src": "research/research-spatial-wayfinding/case-hospital.webp",
      "alt": "Hospital corridor wayfinding — zoned colour system",
      "objectFit": "cover",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": ["10rem", "14rem"],
      "borderRadius": "0.75rem",
      "align": "center",
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "fade",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "c-img-2": {
      "type": "elementImage",
      "src": "research/research-spatial-wayfinding/case-airport.webp",
      "alt": "Airport terminal wayfinding — pictogram system",
      "objectFit": "cover",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": ["10rem", "14rem"],
      "borderRadius": "0.75rem",
      "align": "center",
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "fade",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.07
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "c-img-3": {
      "type": "elementImage",
      "src": "research/research-spatial-wayfinding/case-museum.webp",
      "alt": "Museum wayfinding — typography-first system",
      "objectFit": "cover",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": ["10rem", "14rem"],
      "borderRadius": "0.75rem",
      "align": "center",
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "fade",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.14
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "c-case-1": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Hospital\n\n**Challenge:** Anxiety and disorientation amplify each other. Patients and visitors need to locate destinations quickly under stress.\n\n**Approach:** Colour-coded zones plus redundant text. Decisions forced at corridors, not hallways.",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true
    },
    "c-case-2": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Airport\n\n**Challenge:** Linguistically diverse users, time pressure, high consequence errors (missed flights).\n\n**Approach:** ISO pictogram system supplemented by high-contrast typography. No idioms. Distance indicators everywhere.",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true
    },
    "c-case-3": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### Museum\n\n**Challenge:** Wayfinding must serve without dominating — visitors should feel guided, not managed.\n\n**Approach:** Typography-first. Minimal, high-quality signs placed at decision points only. Designed to recede.",
      "level": 5,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true
    }
  },
  "gridMode": {
    "mobile": "columns",
    "desktop": "grid"
  },
  "gridDebug": false,
